data.description: In the heart of the desired Southeast Polk School District, discover this inviting two-story home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. Enjoy modern upgrades, including new paint on both levels, and new carpet on the second level. The main level offers new LVP flooring, along with new trim and a cozy fireplace. Opening up to a spacious deck with a covered cabana, leading to a heated above-ground pool and a convenient bonus half bath keeping the water out of the house, a backyard oasis to say the least! The kitchen boasts brand-new appliances. Below, the unfinished basement awaits your creative ideas. Make this property your dream home today!
